This patch reuses the existing AggregateFunctionTimeseriesExtrapolatedValue
kernel. It (1) adds a trailing defaulted `is_increase` flag to the Traits,
(2) extends getName(), (3) guards only the divide-by-window, and (4) registers
timeSeriesIncreaseToGrid via an alias that pins is_increase=true so the generic
factory still sees a five-parameter template-template.

